          "description": "Suzuki Shinichi is an animator working previously at Sunrise, where he worked on Gozaurer and Cyber Formula and currently at Magic Bus.\n\n<i>Notes:\n-Not to be confused with the supervisor, mangaka and director [Suzuki Shinichi](https://anilist.co/staff/116321/Shinichi-Suzuki) by the same name, who was most active during 60s-80s.\n-Not to be confused with animator, director and Anime Koubou Basara founder [Suzuki Shinichi](https://anilist.co/staff/116319) by a different kanji name.<i>",
